---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="AdBunny — AI Banner Monetization for Remnant Inventory"
  description="Monetize remnant ad inventory with one JS tag. AdBunny's AI optimizes every banner impression in real time. No waterfall, no dev lift."
  keywords="remnant inventory monetization, banner ad monetization platform, AI ad optimization, programmatic banner ads, unsold ad inventory, single tag ad monetization"
>

<section class="pt-32 pb-20 max-md:pt-20 max-md:pb-14">
  <div class="max-w-[76rem] mx-auto px-8">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-[1.3fr_1fr] gap-16 items-center max-md:grid-cols-1 max-md:gap-10">
      <div>
        <h1 class="text-[clamp(2.5rem,5vw,4rem)] font-extrabold leading-[1.05] tracking-tight mb-5">Turn unsold ad space into <span class="text-accent">revenue</span></h1>
        <p class="text-[1.0625rem] text-text-secondary leading-relaxed mb-8">One tag. AI-driven optimization. Zero conflict with your existing ad stack.</p>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
          <a href="/" class="btn btn-primary">Get Your JS Tag</a>
          <a href="/how-it-works" class="btn btn-ghost">How it works &rarr;</a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="max-md:row-start-1">
        <div class="border border-border" style="background:#1d1d1f">
          <div class="flex gap-1.5 px-4 py-2.5 border-b" style="border-color:rgba(255,255,255,0.06)">
            <span class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-red-500/80"></span>
            <span class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-yellow-500/80"></span>
            <span class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-green-500/80"></span>
          </div>
          <pre class="p-5 font-mono text-xs leading-relaxed overflow-x-auto" style="color:#888;background:#1d1d1f"><code style="color:#ddd">&lt;script src="cdn.adbunny.in/adbunny.js"
  data-publisher="your-tag"
  data-target="#ad-slot"&gt;
&lt;/script&gt;</code></pre>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="flex items-center gap-10 mt-14 pt-14 border-t border-border max-md:flex-col max-md:items-start max-md:gap-5 max-md:mt-10 max-md:pt-10">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
        <span class="text-lg font-bold tracking-tight">394K</span>
        <span class="text-sm text-text-secondary">events / sec</span>
      </div>
      <div class="w-px h-6 bg-border max-md:hidden"></div>
      <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
        <span class="text-lg font-bold tracking-tight">&lt;5 min</span>
        <span class="text-sm text-text-secondary">setup time</span>
      </div>
      <div class="w-px h-6 bg-border max-md:hidden"></div>
      <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
        <span class="text-lg font-bold tracking-tight">89%</span>
        <span class="text-sm text-text-secondary">fill rate</span>
      </div>
      <div class="w-px h-6 bg-border max-md:hidden"></div>
      <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
        <span class="text-lg font-bold tracking-tight">0</span>
        <span class="text-sm text-text-secondary">conflicts</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="border-t border-border border-b border-border bg-elevated">
  <div class="max-w-[76rem] mx-auto px-8 py-5 overflow-hidden">
    <div class="flex" style="width:max-content">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-12 pr-12 text-sm font-medium text-text-tertiary" style="animation:ticker-scroll 30s linear infinite">
        <span>PublisherCo</span><span class="ticker-dot"></span>
        <span>AdNet+</span><span class="ticker-dot"></span>
        <span>MediaServe</span><span class="ticker-dot"></span>
        <span>BannerFlow</span><span class="ticker-dot"></span>
        <span>AdStack</span><span class="ticker-dot"></span>
        <span>Remnant.io</span><span class="ticker-dot"></span>
        <span>PublisherCo</span><span class="ticker-dot"></span>
        <span>AdNet+</span><span class="ticker-dot"></span>
        <span>MediaServe</span><span class="ticker-dot"></span>
        <span>BannerFlow</span><span class="ticker-dot"></span>
        <span>AdStack</span><span class="ticker-dot"></span>
        <span>Remnant.io</span><span class="ticker-dot"></span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="py-24 max-md:py-16">
  <div class="max-w-[76rem] mx-auto px-8">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-[1fr_1fr] gap-20 items-center max-md:grid-cols-1 max-md:gap-10">
      <div>
        <span class="inline-block text-[0.65rem] font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-accent bg-accent-bg border border-accent-border px-[0.625rem] py-[0.25rem] mb-5">For Publishers</span>
        <h2 class="text-[clamp(1.75rem,3vw,2.25rem)] font-bold tracking-tight leading-snug mb-4">Fill remnant slots without touching your demand stack</h2>
        <p class="text-base text-text-secondary leading-relaxed mb-7">One tag. Same-day setup. No conflict with existing demand partners. AdBunny acts as a secondary layer — serving only when your primary stack passes.</p>
        <ul class="list-none flex flex-col gap-[0.625rem] mb-7">
          <li class="flex items-center gap-[0.625rem] text-[0.9375rem] font-medium text-text-secondary"><span class="split-check"></span> No conflict with existing demand</li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-[0.625rem] text-[0.9375rem] font-medium text-text-secondary"><span class="split-check"></span> Same-day setup, no dev sprint</li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-[0.625rem] text-[0.9375rem] font-medium text-text-secondary"><span class="split-check"></span> AI optimizes every impression in real time</li>
        </ul>
        <a href="/publishers" class="split-link">Learn more &rarr;</a>
      </div>
      <div class="flex flex-col gap-4">
        <div class="border border-accent-border bg-accent-bg">
          <div class="px-5 py-3 border-b border-accent-border">
            <span class="text-[0.7rem] font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider text-accent">Fill Rate Improvement</span>
          </div>
          <div class="p-5 flex flex-col gap-2">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3"><span class="w-7 text-[0.7rem] font-medium text-text-tertiary text-right shrink-0">Mon</span><div class="h-7 flex items-center justify-end px-[0.625rem] split-bar--accent" style="width:87%"><span class="text-[0.7rem] font-semibold text-black">87%</span></div></div>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3"><span class="w-7 text-[0.7rem] font-medium text-text-tertiary text-right shrink-0">Tue</span><div class="h-7 flex items-center justify-end px-[0.625rem] split-bar--accent" style="width:91%"><span class="text-[0.7rem] font-semibold text-black">91%</span></div></div>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3"><span class="w-7 text-[0.7rem] font-medium text-text-tertiary text-right shrink-0">Wed</span><div class="h-7 flex items-center justify-end px-[0.625rem] split-bar--accent" style="width:89%"><span class="text-[0.7rem] font-semibold text-black">89%</span></div></div>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3"><span class="w-7 text-[0.7rem] font-medium text-text-tertiary text-right shrink-0">Thu</span><div class="h-7 flex items-center justify-end px-[0.625rem] split-bar--accent" style="width:93%"><span class="text-[0.7rem] font-semibold text-black">93%</span></div></div>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3"><span class="w-7 text-[0.7rem] font-medium text-text-tertiary text-right shrink-0">Fri</span><div class="h-7 flex items-center justify-end px-[0.625rem] split-bar--accent" style="width:88%"><span class="text-[0.7rem] font-semibold text-black">88%</span></div></div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="py-24 bg-elevated border-t border-border border-b border-border max-md:py-16">
  <div class="max-w-[76rem] mx-auto px-8">
    <div class="text-center mb-16 max-md:mb-10">
      <span class="inline-block text-[0.65rem] font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-accent bg-accent-bg border border-accent-border px-[0.625rem] py-[0.25rem] mb-4">Why AdBunny</span>
      <h2 class="text-[clamp(1.75rem,3vw,2.5rem)] font-bold tracking-tight">Built for publishers and ad networks</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="grid grid-cols-3 gap-6 max-md:grid-cols-1">
      <div class="border border-border p-8 hover:bg-surface-hover transition-colors">
        <div class="w-10 h-10 flex items-center justify-center mb-5" style="background:var(--color-accent-bg);color:var(--color-accent)">
          <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 20V10"/><path d="M18 20V4"/><path d="M6 20v-4"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold tracking-tight mb-2">For Publishers</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-text-secondary leading-relaxed mb-6">Fill remnant slots without touching your primary demand stack. One tag, same-day setup, no conflict.</p>
        <a href="/publishers" class="text-sm font-semibold text-accent">Learn more &rarr;</a>
      </div>
      <div class="border border-border p-8 hover:bg-surface-hover transition-colors">
        <div class="w-10 h-10 flex items-center justify-center mb-5" style="background:var(--color-accent-bg);color:var(--color-accent)">
          <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="18" cy="5" r="3"/><circle cx="6" cy="12" r="3"/><circle cx="18" cy="19" r="3"/><line x1="8.59" y1="13.51" x2="15.42" y2="17.49"/><line x1="15.41" y1="6.51" x2="8.59" y2="10.49"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold tracking-tight mb-2">For Ad Networks</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-text-secondary leading-relaxed mb-6">Programmatic access to aggregated remnant banner inventory across the AdBunny network with real-time reporting.</p>
        <a href="/advertisers" class="text-sm font-semibold text-accent">Learn more &rarr;</a>
      </div>
      <div class="border border-border p-8 hover:bg-surface-hover transition-colors">
        <div class="w-10 h-10 flex items-center justify-center mb-5" style="background:var(--color-accent-bg);color:var(--color-accent)">
          <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="3" y="11" width="18" height="11" rx="2" ry="2"/><path d="M7 11V7a5 5 0 0 1 10 0v4"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold tracking-tight mb-2">AI-Driven Optimization</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-text-secondary leading-relaxed mb-6">Our AI evaluates demand per impression in real time, so every banner is the one most likely to pay best right now.</p>
        <a href="/how-it-works" class="text-sm font-semibold text-accent">Learn more &rarr;</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="py-24 max-md:py-16">
  <div class="max-w-[76rem] mx-auto px-8">
    <div class="text-center mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-[clamp(1.5rem,2.5vw,2rem)] font-bold tracking-tight">What our partners say</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="grid grid-cols-3 gap-6 max-md:grid-cols-1">
      <div class="border border-border p-8 bg-surface">
        <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="mb-4" style="color:var(--color-accent);opacity:0.4"><path d="M3 21c3 0 7-1 7-8V5c0-1.25-.756-2.017-2-2H4c-1.25 0-2 .75-2 1.972V11c0 1.25.75 2 2 2 1 0 1 0 1 1v1c0 1-1 2-2 2s-1 .008-1 1.031V21z"/><path d="M15 21c3 0 7-1 7-8V5c0-1.25-.757-2.017-2-2h-4c-1.25 0-2 .75-2 1.972V11c0 1.25.75 2 2 2h.75c0 2.25.25 4-2.75 4v3c0 1 0 1 1 1z"/></svg>
        <p class="text-sm text-text-secondary leading-relaxed mb-6">"AdBunny integrated in minutes and our remnant fill rate went from ~30% to over 85% within the first week. No engineering lift required."</p>
        <div class="border-t border-border pt-4 mt-auto">
          <div class="text-sm font-semibold">Sarah Chen</div>
          <div class="text-xs text-text-secondary">Head of Ad Ops, PublisherCo</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="border border-border p-8 bg-surface">
        <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="mb-4" style="color:var(--color-accent);opacity:0.4"><path d="M3 21c3 0 7-1 7-8V5c0-1.25-.756-2.017-2-2H4c-1.25 0-2 .75-2 1.972V11c0 1.25.75 2 2 2 1 0 1 0 1 1v1c0 1-1 2-2 2s-1 .008-1 1.031V21z"/><path d="M15 21c3 0 7-1 7-8V5c0-1.25-.757-2.017-2-2h-4c-1.25 0-2 .75-2 1.972V11c0 1.25.75 2 2 2h.75c0 2.25.25 4-2.75 4v3c0 1 0 1 1 1z"/></svg>
        <p class="text-sm text-text-secondary leading-relaxed mb-6">"We were skeptical about another ad tag, but AdBunny's AI optimization genuinely outperformed our existing waterfall. Revenue uplift was immediate."</p>
        <div class="border-t border-border pt-4 mt-auto">
          <div class="text-sm font-semibold">Marcus Rivera</div>
          <div class="text-xs text-text-secondary">Director of Monetization, AdNet+</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="border border-border p-8 bg-surface">
        <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="mb-4" style="color:var(--color-accent);opacity:0.4"><path d="M3 21c3 0 7-1 7-8V5c0-1.25-.756-2.017-2-2H4c-1.25 0-2 .75-2 1.972V11c0 1.25.75 2 2 2 1 0 1 0 1 1v1c0 1-1 2-2 2s-1 .008-1 1.031V21z"/><path d="M15 21c3 0 7-1 7-8V5c0-1.25-.757-2.017-2-2h-4c-1.25 0-2 .75-2 1.972V11c0 1.25.75 2 2 2h.75c0 2.25.25 4-2.75 4v3c0 1 0 1 1 1z"/></svg>
        <p class="text-sm text-text-secondary leading-relaxed mb-6">"The single-tag integration meant our engineering team didn't need to do anything. It just worked. The reporting dashboard gave us immediate visibility."</p>
        <div class="border-t border-border pt-4 mt-auto">
          <div class="text-sm font-semibold">Priya Patel</div>
          <div class="text-xs text-text-secondary">VP Product, BannerFlow</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="py-12 overflow-hidden border-t border-border border-b border-border bg-elevated">
  <div class="flex overflow-hidden">
    <div class="flex gap-8 whitespace-nowrap" style="animation:marquee-left 30s linear infinite">
      <span class="text-[clamp(2rem,4vw,3.5rem)] font-extrabold tracking-tight" style="color:transparent;-webkit-text-stroke:1px rgba(0,0,0,0.1)">Monetize remnant inventory</span>
      <span class="marquee-star">*</span>
      <span class="text-[clamp(2rem,4vw,3.5rem)] font-extrabold tracking-tight" style="color:transparent;-webkit-text-stroke:1px rgba(0,0,0,0.1)">AI-driven banner optimization</span>
      <span class="marquee-star">*</span>
      <span class="text-[clamp(2rem,4vw,3.5rem)] font-extrabold tracking-tight" style="color:transparent;-webkit-text-stroke:1px rgba(0,0,0,0.1)">One JS tag integration</span>
      <span class="marquee-star">*</span>
      <span class="text-[clamp(2rem,4vw,3.5rem)] font-extrabold tracking-tight" style="color:transparent;-webkit-text-stroke:1px rgba(0,0,0,0.1)">Zero conflict with your stack</span>
      <span class="marquee-star">*</span>
      <span class="text-[clamp(2rem,4vw,3.5rem)] font-extrabold tracking-tight" style="color:transparent;-webkit-text-stroke:1px rgba(0,0,0,0.1)">Monetize remnant inventory</span>
      <span class="marquee-star">*</span>
      <span class="text-[clamp(2rem,4vw,3.5rem)] font-extrabold tracking-tight" style="color:transparent;-webkit-text-stroke:1px rgba(0,0,0,0.1)">AI-driven banner optimization</span>
      <span class="marquee-star">*</span>
      <span class="text-[clamp(2rem,4vw,3.5rem)] font-extrabold tracking-tight" style="color:transparent;-webkit-text-stroke:1px rgba(0,0,0,0.1)">One JS tag integration</span>
      <span class="marquee-star">*</span>
      <span class="text-[clamp(2rem,4vw,3.5rem)] font-extrabold tracking-tight" style="color:transparent;-webkit-text-stroke:1px rgba(0,0,0,0.1)">Zero conflict with your stack</span>
      <span class="marquee-star">*</span>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="py-24 max-md:py-16">
  <div class="max-w-[76rem] mx-auto px-8">
    <div class="flex items-center justify-between gap-12 p-16 max-md:flex-col max-md:text-center max-md:p-12 bg-elevated" style="border:1px solid var(--color-border-strong)">
      <div class="relative max-w-[30rem] z-10 max-md:max-w-full">
        <h2 class="text-[clamp(1.75rem,2.5vw,2.25rem)] font-bold tracking-tight mb-3 leading-snug">Stop leaving remnant revenue on the table</h2>
        <p class="text-base text-text-secondary leading-relaxed">One tag. AI-driven optimization. Revenue from inventory that used to sit empty.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="shrink-0 z-10">
        <a href="/" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">
          Get Your JS Tag
          <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><line x1="5" y1="12" x2="19" y2="12"/><polyline points="12 5 19 12 12 19"/></svg>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="pb-24 max-md:pb-16">
  <div class="max-w-[76rem] mx-auto px-8">
    <div class="text-center mb-12">
      <span class="inline-block text-[0.65rem] font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-accent bg-accent-bg border border-accent-border px-[0.625rem] py-[0.25rem] mb-4">FAQ</span>
      <h2 class="text-[clamp(1.5rem,2.5vw,2rem)] font-bold tracking-tight">Frequently asked questions</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="max-w-[44rem] mx-auto">
      <div class="border-b border-border">
        <button class="faq-q w-full text-left bg-transparent border-none py-5 text-[0.9375rem] font-semibold cursor-pointer flex justify-between items-center gap-4 text-text hover:text-accent transition-colors">Will AdBunny conflict with my existing ad stack?</button>
        <div class="faq-a overflow-hidden transition-[max-height] duration-300 ease" style="max-height:0"><div class="pb-5 text-[0.9375rem] text-text-secondary leading-relaxed">No. AdBunny is built to run on remnant inventory only, so it fills what your primary demand doesn't reach. There's no conflict because AdBunny acts as a secondary layer — it only serves ads when your primary stack passes on an impression.</div></div>
      </div>
      <div class="border-b border-border">
        <button class="faq-q w-full text-left bg-transparent border-none py-5 text-[0.9375rem] font-semibold cursor-pointer flex justify-between items-center gap-4 text-text hover:text-accent transition-colors">How long does setup take?</button>
        <div class="faq-a overflow-hidden transition-[max-height] duration-300 ease" style="max-height:0"><div class="pb-5 text-[0.9375rem] text-text-secondary leading-relaxed">Typically minutes. It's one JS tag — not a waterfall, not an SDK integration, not a server-side change. Paste the tag into your pages or ad slots and you're live.</div></div>
      </div>
      <div class="border-b border-border">
        <button class="faq-q w-full text-left bg-transparent border-none py-5 text-[0.9375rem] font-semibold cursor-pointer flex justify-between items-center gap-4 text-text hover:text-accent transition-colors">What kind of fill rates can I expect?</button>
        <div class="faq-a overflow-hidden transition-[max-height] duration-300 ease" style="max-height:0"><div class="pb-5 text-[0.9375rem] text-text-secondary leading-relaxed">Our network average is ~89% fill rate on remnant inventory, compared to ~35% with traditional static waterfalls. Results vary by traffic and inventory, but most publishers see an immediate uplift.</div></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

</BaseLayout>
